text: Fok Ming Shan is an archer from Hong Kong. He was born on 5 July 1958. Ming Shan competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics.Fok Ming ShanMing-Chan FOK == References == Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:Hong Kong archers Category:Olympians for Hong Kong
